# OUTPUT-DRIVEN, two stages: 1 electronic circuit per second.
# Circuits eat 3 cables/craft -> both stages multi-copy, each circuit machine
# gets its own dedicated cable lane (multi-arm as separate same-product lanes).
input copper : copper-plate
input iron : iron-plate
assembler cable : copper-cable
assembler circuit : electronic-circuit
output chips @ 1/s

copper -> cable
cable -> circuit
iron -> circuit
circuit -> chips
